							<h5><a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/11/30/teds-science-curator-sees-hope-in-the-anthropocene/" title="Read: TED&#8217;s Science Curator Sees Hope in Earth&#8217;s Anthropocene Age">TED&#8217;s Science Curator Sees Hope in Earth&#8217;s Anthropocene Age</a>
